        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated based on literature data published by the GENDORF Chemical Park. The factory produced an average of 2462760 tonnes of chemical substances (including intermediates) per year in the years 2015-2019. The average consumption of steam (internal and external sources) in the years 2015-2019 was 511785800 MJ per year. This equals 0.2078 MJ/kg chemical produced.

